race.description: Parma Pot Luck Deal At Wbl Greys (300+)
race.comment: BELAIR BLUE (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (22.50) in a Grade 5 at this track. Has ability and is a key runner. BERT DEEDS (2) turned in a fair run last time from the squeeze finishing fifth by 4.5 lengths (22.88). Has ability and can atone. BRINDLE BEC (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (26.60) in a Grade 5 at this track. One of the better chances. MIRA BALE (8) is right in the mix.
